Film star Bolanle Ninalowo has applauded himself for metamorphosing over the years into his best version. The 41-year-old movie producer, in a post on social media, explained before he arrived at this version of himself, he underwent pain and agony. According to Maka, at this point of his life, he can boldly declare himself his own inspiration.   Why crime is high among youths – M.I Abaga     Only women can brag about s3x- Okon Lagos     I lost self-confidence after scarred face – Sonia Ogiri   Ninalowo wrote: “The way I changed my life around over the years for the better! To become a better version of me! - Advertisement - “Now I am my own inspiration. The pain & agony it took thou!! I took responsibility, I Choose differently & the best version of me now in the making! “Thank you Bolanle. May God’s Grace never cease. Maka.” SPONSORED